Global IR Remote Receiver Market Insights
IR Remote Receiver Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.8% from 2024 to 2030.

IR Remote Receiver Market Overview
The global IR Remote Receiver market was valued at approximately USD 3.5 billion in 2024 and is expected to expand at a CAGR of 7.2% over the forecast period. The growth of the market is driven by the increasing demand for remote-controlled devices in consumer electronics, automotive, and industrial applications. IR Remote Receivers are crucial in enabling wireless communication between electronic devices, making them an essential part of modern technology. Furthermore, the expanding consumer electronics sector, particularly with the rise of smart home devices, continues to boost market growth.

